  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Module

    public class ZDTModule
extends ProblemModule
    The ZDTModule configures the ZDT benchmarks, see "Comparison of Multiobjective Evolutionary Algorithms: Empirical Results, Eckart Zitzler, Kalyanmoy Deb, Lothar Thiele, Evolutionary Computation Volume 8 , Issue 2 (June 2000)".
